Moneyweb has appointed Suren Naidoo as its new deputy editor. Naidoo has been a senior Moneyweb journalist since 2019. He has covered critical developments in several industries, including the property, retail, and tourism sectors. Subscribe for full access to all our share and unit trust data tools, our award-winning articles, and support quality journalism in the process. You will be redirected to a checkout page.
