A yearly subscription is refundable within 14 days of purchase and includes a 365-day membership. Before joining Moneyweb, Naidoo was the business editor of The Mercury in KwaZulu-Natal. He was also an entrepreneur and a media manager in the public relations industry. “Suren is an experienced and respected journalist and an invaluable member of the Moneyweb team. He is the ideal candidate to lead the news team and to ensure that Moneyweb remains the country’s leading business, financial and investment content hub, says Ryk van Niekerk, Moneyweb’s editor. “Moneyweb’s pedigree as a pioneering and trusted online financial news source goes back more than two decades. I have always been a fan, and this is a great opportunity to contribute to the further growth of the Moneyweb brand,” says Naidoo. He will assume the role from July 1.    